Class SemanticSearchBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ctakes.ytex.web.search.SemanticSearchBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class SemanticSearchBean
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    JSF Backing Bean for semanticSearch.jspx. Search for documents based on concept ids, negation status, patient, and date. Based on the IceFaces autocomplete example.
